data.description: Immaculate single-level home in a private cul-de-sac on the Dry Canyon. The backyard contains an easy path down to enjoy the park and all the amenities the dry canyon has to offer--incredible views from Dinning, Living, and Master Bedrooms. Entertainers dream with a heated bright Sunroom looking out to the entertainer's dream backyard--fully fenced RV parking with an easy access gate. The home is close to downtown Redmond and the center of the community amenities--Assumable VA loan for a low-interest rate. Also just announced that 17th Street will be connecting to make for a great entrance to the house.
